comment: In short, the running count of missing terms in A247665.

maple: # computes first M terms, assumes b1 is list of first M terms of A247665
for n from 1 to M do
for i from last+1 to t1-1 do
if not member(i,A) and not member(i,miss) then miss:=[op(miss),i]; nom:=nom+1; fi;
